/d/99003/" data-original="https://img.tupian-zuida.com/pic/upload/vod/2019-08-19/201908191566173515.jpg"><span class="fed-list-play fed-hide-xs"></span><span class="fed-list-score fed-font-xii fed-back-green">2.0</span><span class="fed-list-remarks fed-font-xii fed-text-white fed-text-center">HD1024高清中字版</span></a></dt><dd class="fed-deta-content fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-col-md10"><h1 class="fed-part-eone fed-font-xvi"><a href="/d/99003/">僵尸暴龙</a></h1><ul class="fed-part-rows"><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">主演：</span><a href="/s/-%E5%86%85%E8%AF%A6------------/" target="_blank">内详</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">导演：</span><a href="/s/-----Milko--------/" target="_blank">Milko</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-----Davis--------/" target="_blank">Davis</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-----Main--------/" target="_blank">Main</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-----Director--------/" target="_blank">Director</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">分类：</span><a href="/vodtype/10/" target="_blank">恐怖片</a></li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">地区：</span><a href="/s/--%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD-----------/" target="_blank">美国</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">年份：</span><a href="/s/-------------2018/" target="_blank">2018</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">更新：</span>2019.08.23</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-hide fed-show-md-block"><div class="fed-part-esan"><span class="fed-text-muted">简介：</span>一名破解科学家与邪恶轴心一致，用EMP爆炸物，有毒的僵化气体以及最终的不死生物杀死怪物--Z-REX释放A的美国当一个热线民兵队和一群大学时髦人员被扔在一起做一些事情时，混乱的捕食者 - 雷霆行动就会横行。&nbsp;</div></li></ul></dd><dd class="fed-deta-button fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-part-rows"><a class="fed-deta-play fed-rims-info fed-btns-info fed-btns-green fed-col-xs4" href="/d/99003/">查看详情</a></dd></dl><dl class="fed-deta-info fed-deta-padding fed-line-top fed-margin fed-part-rows fed-part-over"><dt class="fed-deta-images fed-list-info fed-col-xs3"><a class="fed-list-pics fed-lazy fed-part-2by3" href="/d/37247/" data-original="http://cj.subo8988.com:8988/upload/vod/2018-11-21/201811211542792747.jpg"><span class="fed-list-play fed-hide-xs"></span><span class="fed-list-score fed-font-xii fed-back-green">10.0</span><span class="fed-list-remarks fed-font-xii fed-text-white fed-text-center">HD</span></a></dt><dd class="fed-deta-content fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-col-md10"><h1 class="fed-part-eone fed-font-xvi"><a href="/d/37247/">僵尸少爷</a></h1><ul class="fed-part-rows"><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">主演：</span><a href="/s/-%E8%91%A3%E9%AA%A0------------/" target="_blank">董骠</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E6%9E%97%E7%A7%80%E5%90%9B------------/" target="_blank">林秀君</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E5%B0%8F%E5%A5%87%E5%A5%87------------/" target="_blank">小奇奇</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">导演：</span><a href="/s/-----%E5%88%98%E6%B3%B3%E5%9F%BA--------/" target="_blank">刘泳基</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-------------/" target="_blank"></a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">分类：</span><a href="/vodtype/10/" target="_blank">恐怖片</a></li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">地区：</span><a href="/s/--%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-----------/" target="_blank">香港</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">年份：</span><a href="/s/-------------1986/" target="_blank">1986</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">更新：</span>2019.08.20</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-hide fed-show-md-block"><div class="fed-part-esan"><span class="fed-text-muted">简介：</span>调皮捣蛋的小僵尸乃僵尸家族的宠儿，某夜突然失去踪影，家族成员四处寻找僵尸小爷途中遇一青年阿贵，阿鬼明知他非人类，欲将他送回家。有一茅山道人，专门利用夜间偷刚死的尸体，炼成僵尸，为非作歹，无意中得知阿鬼有一僵尸仔，乃千方百计欲夺取....</div></li></ul></dd><dd class="fed-deta-button fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-part-rows"><a class="fed-deta-play fed-rims-info fed-btns-info fed-btns-green fed-col-xs4" href="/d/37247/">查看详情</a></dd></dl><dl class="fed-deta-info fed-deta-padding fed-line-top fed-margin fed-part-rows fed-part-over"><dt class="fed-deta-images fed-list-info fed-col-xs3"><a class="fed-list-pics fed-lazy fed-part-2by3" href="/d/12118/" data-original="http://pic.iqiyi6123.com/upload/vod/2019-01-17/15477154459.jpg"><span class="fed-list-play fed-hide-xs"></span><span class="fed-list-score fed-font-xii fed-back-green">1.0</span><span class="fed-list-remarks fed-font-xii fed-text-white fed-text-center"></span></a></dt><dd class="fed-deta-content fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-col-md10"><h1 class="fed-part-eone fed-font-xvi"><a href="/d/12118/">僵尸之地</a></h1><ul class="fed-part-rows"><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">主演：</span><a href="/s/-%E6%B3%B0%E5%8B%92%C2%B7%E7%BD%97%E6%96%AF------------/" target="_blank">泰勒·罗斯</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E7%8E%9B%E4%BE%9D%E4%BA%9A%E6%8B%89%C2%B7%E6%B2%83%E5%B0%94%E4%BB%80------------/" target="_blank">玛依亚拉·沃尔什</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E4%BC%8A%E6%89%8E%E8%B4%9D%E6%8B%89%C2%B7%E7%BB%B4%E5%A4%9A%E7%BB%B4%E5%A5%87------------/" target="_blank">伊扎贝拉·维多维奇</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E8%92%82%E5%A7%86%C2%B7%E5%B7%B4%E6%A0%BC%E8%8E%B1------------/" target="_blank">蒂姆·巴格莱</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">导演：</span><a href="/s/-----%E8%89%BE%E5%88%A9%C2%B7%E5%85%8B%E9%9B%B7%E6%A0%BC--------/" target="_blank">艾利·克雷格</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">分类：</span><a href="/vodtype/10/" target="_blank">恐怖片</a></li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">地区：</span><a href="/s/--%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD-----------/" target="_blank">美国</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">年份：</span><a href="/s/-------------2013/" target="_blank">2013</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">更新：</span>2019.08.20</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-hide fed-show-md-block"><div class="fed-part-esan"><span class="fed-text-muted">简介：</span>根据2009年同名影片改编的电视剧集播出一集後，亚马逊网正式放弃拍摄和制作美剧《僵尸之地》，因为观众对试映集的反应并不太热情。创作人将这归罪于原版电影爱好者不给面子！</div></li></ul></dd><dd class="fed-deta-button fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-part-rows"><a class="fed-deta-play fed-rims-info fed-btns-info fed-btns-green fed-col-xs4" href="/d/12118/">查看详情</a></dd></dl><dl class="fed-deta-info fed-deta-padding fed-line-top fed-margin fed-part-rows fed-part-over"><dt class="fed-deta-images fed-list-info fed-col-xs3"><a class="fed-list-pics fed-lazy fed-part-2by3" href="/d/51217/" data-original="http://cj.subo8988.com:8988/upload/vod/2018-12-22/201812221545464417.jpg"><span class="fed-list-play fed-hide-xs"></span><span class="fed-list-score fed-font-xii fed-back-green">7.0</span><span class="fed-list-remarks fed-font-xii fed-text-white fed-text-center">HD</span></a></dt><dd class="fed-deta-content fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-col-md10"><h1 class="fed-part-eone fed-font-xvi"><a href="/d/51217/">僵尸先生2</a></h1><ul class="fed-part-rows"><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">主演：</span><a href="/s/-%E6%9E%97%E6%AD%A3%E8%8B%B1------------/" target="_blank">林正英</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E5%85%83%E5%BD%AA------------/" target="_blank">元彪</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">导演：</span><a href="/s/-----%E5%88%98%E8%A7%82%E4%BC%9F--------/" target="_blank">刘观伟</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">分类：</span><a href="/vodtype/10/" target="_blank">恐怖片</a></li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted"